Options:
eap_method: [peap,eap,md5,...]
ca_cert_path: /path/to/nonsystem/cert.crt
inner_method: [peap,eap,md5,...]
connection_name: [enp0s3,auto,...]

Note: These settings will be ignored if NetworkManager is already configured for 802.1x

Example:
password pam_8021x.so eap_method=peap ca_cert_path=/path/to/nonsystem/cert.crt inner_method=mschapv2 connection_name=enp0s3
